    Team - Class in League
    Represents a single Team in the league, holding details such as its name, the players assigned to it, the coaches assigned to it, its home ground stadium etc.
    Team(String) - Constructor for class League.Team
    Constructs the Team object with the specified name, the players and coaches array lists are also initialised when this constructor is called
    TeamManager - Class in League
    Represents a singular team manager assigned to a team present in the league, including details such as name, team, and employment status
    TeamManager(String) - Constructor for class League.TeamManager
    Constructs the TeamManager object with the specified name, TeamManager inherits the attributes name, and employmentStatus from its parent Person class along with their getter and setter methods
